
Project: Simplified Blog Website
This will be a multi-page website with:
 * A homepage displaying recent blog posts (static content for now).
 * Individual pages for each blog post.
 * A navigation bar to move between pages.
 * A responsive design to look good on different screen sizes.
 * JavaScript interactivity for potential features (e.g., a simple theme toggle).
